  49. ‌let export_caml_ld_library_path value =
  50.   let current_value = Sys.safe_getenv caml_ld_library_path_name in
  51.   let local_value =
  52.     (String.concat Filename.path_sep (String.words value)) in
  53. ‌  let new_value =
  54.     if local_value="" then current_value else
  55.     if current_value="" then local_value else
  56.     String.concat Filename.path_sep [local_value; current_value] in
  57.   (caml_ld_library_path_name, new_value)
